item.title: Dood Village NP Bingo Request
item.content:encoded: Hello, kind sir and or madam! Thank you for taking a look at my humble request. I'm a member of the Dood village, and I would like to ask that somebody out there NP bingo me, as I need Anonymous. As of writing this, I am a lvl 73, S2 Sannin. If you do, in fact, bingo me with the note, I will be greatly appreciative, and will help NP bingo you if possible. Thanks!
